lyrics:
Vana ka kumkhaw in chu,
Mawi ropui a ni;
Chutah hlim teh sen loh
Zan thim a awm ngai lo;
Puan var sin vantirhkohten,
Pathian fakin hla an sa;
Aw, eng tik nge ka hmuh ang,
Nang, vana ka in mawi chu?

Van in mawi tak chu,
Van in lawmawm chu;
Kan Chhandamtu awmna,
Van in mawi tak chu.

Chumi hmun mawi takah chuan,
Pangpar an par fo;
Kan Lal Isua fakin,
Naupangten zai an rem;
An hla sak a va mawi em!
Thutphah ropui velah khian;
Aw, eng tik nge ka hmuh ang,
Nang, vana ka in mawi chu?

Ram mawia tlan sa zingah,
Ka tel ve thuai dawn;
Krista, ka Chhandamtu,
Eng nge thih ka hlauh vang?
Thutphah ropuia thuin,
Ka Lal ka hmu thuai dawn si;
Aw, chu mi hmun ngeiah chuan,
Van in mawi, ka hmu ang che.
